name: Visage Of The Emperor
Lore: 'Palpatine''s hologram. Imposing. Ominous. Intimidating. Instrument for the evil Emperor''s sinister reach across the galaxy. Used on a secret frequency of the Imperial HoloNet.',
Text: 'Lose 2 Force to deploy on Executor: Holotheatre or Death Star: Conference Room. At the end of each player''s turn, each player must lost 1 Force. Effect canceled if opponent controls this site. (Immune to Alter.)',
